Package org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.hbase.functions

Contains Flink functions related to HBase.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildEdgeMutation<E extends EPGMEdge,V extends EPGMVertex>
    Creates HBase Mutation from persistent edge data using edge data handler.
    BuildGraphHeadMutation
    Creates HBase Mutation from persistent graph data using graph data handler.
    BuildGraphTransactions
    Co-groups graph-id, vertex-id) and (graph-id, edge-id) tuples to (graph-id, {vertex-id}, {edge-id}) triples\ Forwarded fields first: f0: graph id Read fields first: f1: vertex id Read fields second: f1: edge id
    BuildPersistentEdge<V extends EPGMVertex,E extends EPGMEdge>
    Creates persistent edge data objects from edge data and source/target vertex data.
    BuildPersistentGraphHead<G extends EPGMGraphHead>
    Creates persistent graph data from graph data and vertex/edge identifiers.
    BuildPersistentVertex<V extends EPGMVertex,E extends EPGMEdge>
    Used to create persistent vertex data from vertex data and outgoing/incoming edge data.
    BuildVertexDataWithEdges<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>
    Co-group (vertex-data) with (vertex-id, [out-edge]) to (vertex-data, [out-edge]).
    BuildVertexMutation<V extends EPGMVertex,E extends EPGMEdge>
    Creates HBase Mutation from persistent vertex data using vertex data handler.
    EdgeSet<E extends EPGMEdge>
    Takes grouped edges as input and outputs a tuple containing either source or target vertex id and the edges.
    EdgeSetBySourceId<E extends Edge>
    Takes grouped edges as input and outputs a tuple containing source vertex id and the edges.
    EdgeSetByTargetId<E extends Edge>
    Takes grouped edges as input and outputs a tuple containing target vertex id and the edges.
